<HEADLINE>
EDS: FIXES HEADLINE 
COWBOYS REACH 53-MAN LIMIT, MORE MOVES LIKELY
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By CLARENCE E. HILL JR. 
c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
