the New York Times Syndicate at 1-732-390-4480; fax, 732-390-4697;
e-mail: weyded(at)nytimes.com.)
<TEXT>
<P>
   GEEZERS-RULE _ These days, not only does wisdom come with age,
so do sex appeal and confidence. The media and pop culture _ hand
in hand, like king and queen _ have ruled that aging ain't so bad.
</P>
