<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-28 15:56 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4348 &Cx1f; tab-z
u a BC-ARGENTINA-DIGITAL-DIV     08-28 0350
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ARGENTINA-DIGITAL-DIVIDE-AND-MORE-HARVARD-BUSINESS-REVIEW-ADV-NY </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
TSF 
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; ATTENTION EDITORS: The following articles from Harvard Business
