40-year-old entrepreneur based in Madrid, Spain, who has founded
six high-tech companies over the past two decades. Having made his
fortune, Varsavsky is now applying his entrepreneurial expertise to
the philanthropic work of closing the digital divide in his native
Argentina. A Q&AMP;A. 700 words. By Margaret Hanshaw.
