<P>
   &UR; INTERNATIONAL (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   US-COLOMBIA (Bogota) _ On the eve of President Clinton's arrival
here, the United States and Colombia face a dilemma in fighting a
drug war and insurgents without making human rights a casualty. By
Richard Chacon. 1200 words.
</P>
<P>
