movie sequel to ``The Silence of the Lambs.'' The plot features a
pack of man-eating pigs. The 15 winners were raised in Winnipeg,
Manitoba. ``They really don't attack,'' trainer  &UR; Sled Reynolds &LR; 
told Entertainment Weekly. ``They're just trained to go grab stuff.
I mean, if they're crazy, how do you work around them?''
