 &UR; Bridges &LR; , whose credits include ``The Paper Chase'' and ``The China
Syndrome.'' The Advocate reports that Larson's poems to Bridges,
set to music by  &UR; Ned Rorem &LR; , are on a new Los Angeles Chamber
Orchestra CD, ``More Than a Day.''
